| v3.3 | 2026-04-15 | Prompt self-improvement hardening: upgraded `prompt-self-improvement-pass.md` to v2.1, upgraded bootstrap prompt to v2.1 with status-file truth precedence, and upgraded closure campaign prompt to v3.2 with explicit stale-assumption reconciliation against status/checkpoint/log artifacts |
