| v5.0 | 2026-04-16 | Added `absolute-forensic-closure-campaign.md` as the strict final closure layer with zero-trust validation, mandatory inventory-vs-coverage diffing, hard closure gates, required durable file updates, and explicit closure verdict/report contract |
| v5.1 | 2026-04-16 | Upgraded `live-credentialed-parity-pass.md` into an operator-grade live parity contract with mandatory role credential matrix, shared target tuple, evidence manifest, live safety rules, and deterministic blocker output; added `templates/live-credentialed-parity-template.md`; tightened deterministic-gap closure wording accordingly |
| v5.2 | 2026-04-16 | Added `no-expenses-spared-final-closure-campaign.md` as an adversarial final-sweep layer that hardcodes current uncovered blocker families, forces inventory-vs-coverage re-diffing, and requires a dedicated `no-expenses-spared-final-closure-report.md` before any “nothing left” claim |

