I found a subtler provenance wrinkle in the role services: when the active run semester and `batches.currentSemester` diverge, the faculty/HoD “default” proof view is rebuilt from the latest playback-accessible checkpoint for that semester, then relabeled as run-level provenance. I’m checking whether the maps already name that stage-backed-but-run-labeled behavior; if not, it needs to be recorded as a same-truth drift risk.
