    14	- This pass closes those three families locally in code; the remaining backend provenance blockers are now live runtime proof, not missing local ownership or helper-lineage mapping.
    15	
    16	## Primary Evidence
    17	
    18	- Migration runner and seed orchestration: `air-mentor-api/src/db/migrate.ts`, `air-mentor-api/src/db/seed.ts`
    19	- Schema and migrations: `air-mentor-api/src/db/schema.ts`, `air-mentor-api/src/db/migrations/0006_msruas_proof_runtime.sql` through `0018_proof_active_operational_semester.sql`
    20	- Queue and worker chain: `air-mentor-api/src/lib/proof-run-queue.ts`, `air-mentor-api/src/app.ts`
